high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter near the toilet.
Pick up the bar of soap on the back of the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn left and hang a right at the wall to face the left sink.
Put the bar of soap into the sink, rinse it off a few seconds and then remove the bar from the sink.
Turn around, walk to the wall and turn around again to face the cabinets.
Put the bar of soap on the right side inside the bottom far left cabinet and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean bar of soap inside a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and face the sink on the right.
Pick the soap up from the counter to the right of the sink.
Go left and turn right to face the sink on the left.
Put the soap in the sink and turn the water on and then off and then pick up the soap from the sink.
Back up and face the lower cabinets on the far left.
Put the soap in the cabinet on the far left and then shut the door.
Turn around and stand to the left of the toilet.
Pick up the bar of soap from the counter.
Move the the left and stand in front of the left sink.
Rinse the soap in the sink.
Open the cabinet on the far left.
Put the soap in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put rinsed soap in the cabinet on the far left.
